cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper presents a novel approach for robust manipulation of deformable objects using a controller that maps visual features to control actions of a manipulator. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the approach uses visual features of the cloth to control the manipulator. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the approach uses a random forest-based controller that is trained using an imitation learning approach. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also possible as the approach involves learning a control policy for cloth manipulation. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is less likely but still possible as the paper presents a control approach for manipulating deformable objects.
